Text:
High quality cam, nothing more.. also the audio is pretty bad. 

Thanks 4 the upload, but NO this is not a R5 bud...

Hey dilwad, this *is* indeed an R5--at low res. 

Good video (considering the resolution), fair audio. Audio sounds bassy, recompressed, echoey (is that a word?) but not too bad. Thanks man!
Hmm, after watching some of this, the audio isn't that bad after all. Bassiness can be mostly removed with your tone and vol controls, and the hollow sound really is minimal.
